{{ctx.prefix}}embed {{r = vroll('1d100')}} -title "{{get('name','Someone')}} pulls out a bean from {{get('their', 'their')}} Bag of Beans!" -f "Roll|{{r}}" {{r=r.total}} -f "Result|{{f'''{roll('5d4')} toadstools sprout. If a creature eats a toadstool, roll any die. On an odd roll, the eater must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 5d6 poison damage and become poisoned for 1 hour. On an even roll, the eater gains 5d6 temporary hit points for 1 hour.''' if r==1 else f'''A geyser erupts and spouts water, beer, berry juice, tea, vinegar, wine, or oil (GM's choice) 30 feet into the air for {roll('1d12')} rounds.''' if r<10 else f'''A treant sprouts. There's a 50 percent chance that the treant is chaotic evil and attacks.''' if r<21 else f'''An animate, immobile stone statue in your likeness rises. It makes verbal threats against you. If you leave it and others come near, it describes you as the most heinous of villains and directs the newcomers to find and attack you. If you are on the same plane of existence as the statue, it knows where you are. The statue becomes inanimate after 24 hours.''' if r<31 else f'''A campfire with blue flames springs forth and burns for 24 hours (or until it is extinguished).''' if r<41 else f'''{(ss:=roll('1d6+6'))} shriekers sprout!''' if r<51 else f'''{roll('1d4+8')} bright pink toads crawl forth. Whenever a toad is touched, it transforms into a Large or smaller monster of the GM's choice. The monster remains for 1 minute, then disappears in a puff of bright pink smoke.''' if r<61 else f'''A hungry bulette burrows up and attacks!''' if r<71 else f'''A fruit tree grows. It has {roll('1d10+20')} fruit, {roll('1d8')} of which act as randomly determined magic potions, while one acts as an ingested poison of the GM's choice. The tree vanishes after 1 hour. Picked fruit remains, retaining any magic for 30 days.''' if r<81 else f'''A nest of {roll('1d4+3')} eggs springs up. Any creature that eats an egg must make a DC 20 Constitution saving throw. On a successful save, a creature permanently increases its lowest ability score by 1, randomly choosing among equally low scores. On a failed save, the creature takes 10d6 force damage from an internal magical explosion.''' if r<91 else f'''A pyramid with a 60-foot‐square base bursts upward. Inside is a sarcophagus containing a mummy lord. The pyramid is treated as the mummy lord's lair, and its sarcophagus contains treasure of the GM's choice.''' if r<100 else f'''A giant beanstalk sprouts, growing to a height of the GM's choice. The top leads where the GM chooses, such as to a great view, a cloud giant's castle, or a different plane of existence.'''}}" -thumb https://media-waterdeep.cursecdn.com/avatars/thumbnails/7/116/1000/1000/636284707516440810.jpeg -footer "{{ctx.prefix+ctx.alias}}"
{{f'{ctx.prefix}i madd treant -name "Trent"' if combat() and 9<r<21 else f'{ctx.prefix}i madd shrieker -n {ss}' if combat() and 40<r<51 else f'{ctx.prefix}i madd bulette' if combat() and 60<r<71 else ''}}